```
Let's assume it's on line `N`. I'll use `sed` to insert the resize call before it.

```bash
sed -i 'N i\    Order.resize(Builder.getVF().getKnownMinValue());' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp
```
