`grep -n "Rdx->getReductionOrder(Order);" llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp`
returns `20178:    Rdx->getReductionOrder(Order);`

So I will use `sed` to insert the line at 20178.

```bash
sed -i '20178i\    Order.resize(Builder.getVF().getKnownMinValue());' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp
```
This should fix the crash.

